21 NEW SECTION. Section 2. Appropriation. (1) There is appropriated $6 million from the state
22 special revenue account created in 50-1-119 to the department of public health and human services for the
23 biennium beginning July 1, 2025. The funds may be used only to reimburse counties for the costs of holding in
24 confinement in detention centers individuals who are awaiting evaluation or examination under 46-14-101, 46-
25 14-202, 46-14-221, or 46-14-311, or who have been committed to the custody of the director of public health
26 and human services and are awaiting placement in appropriate facilities pursuant to 46-14-221, 46-14-301, 46-
27 14-302, 46-14-304, 46-14-312, or 46-19-101.
28 (2) The legislature intends that this is a one-time-only appropriation.
